-----------------------------------------------------------------------
--
-- Combat game mode 
--
-- Players buy units at start of each round and fight to eliminate all opposing units.
-- Capturing the central outpost begins (or resets) the countdown timer.
-- A round ends when all units/resources of one team are exhausted or the timer expires.
-- The team with the most surviving units wins the round. 
-- The team that first wins a threshold number of rounds wins the match. 
--
-- (c) Relic Entertainment 2017
--
-----------------------------------------------------------------------


import("cardinal.scar")

